The regulated area can be divided by calculating the variation of voltage caused by the change of output power of DESSs. Therefore, the power flow calculation method can be introduced. The P-Q decomposition equation for the power flow calculation of complex power systems is11ΔPΔQ=∂P∂δ∂P∂V∂Q∂δ∂Q∂VΔδΔV\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
